Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here is out playing around at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:45.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to exact punishment.{FOTC: Then you need to be punished.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:50.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Angel harmless now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:05.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:11.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade never drew her blade on us before we showed signs of resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:16.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:22.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, form a semi{\fnNyala}{\fnNyala}-{\fn}{\fn}circle around her! {皆、半円に取り囲め！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you giving orders? {Noda}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:25.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's protected by Distortion, just attack! {stfu noda!!}{集中砲火だ！＿＿＿で＿＿ようが＿＿＿が勝てる！}{FOTC: Even if she's protected by Distortion, just attack!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are? {Noda}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! {Noda}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:30.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,<sign: Medical Offices (Currently Closed) - Nurse's Office> {I forget do we use health room or nurse or what}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kanade going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite a deep wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even fatal injuries will heal up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:03.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could there be two of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:06.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this world become even more messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:08.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:12.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the Angel Area Invasion mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We found some skill development software on her computer right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a number of powers we'd never seen listed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:24.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one skill called "Harmonics". She activated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harmonics...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of power is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you looking at the screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a skill that splits her into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, a clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:41.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this skill is something Angel developed herself using that software?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:45.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the other one didn't feel like she was quite the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:47.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was way more aggressive than this Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade wouldn't use a skill for any reason other than to protect herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she used her blade, it was just to ricochet our shots.{跳弾させるためだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:58.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you people are one useless bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With the exception of Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be a bunch of idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider this possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:11.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose that when she created that clone, she had a strong offensive intent in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:13.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:16.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:20.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So the clone is continuing to obey the original's command from back then, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:24.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanade herself wouldn't go on an all{\fnNyala}-{\fn}out assault like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:28.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it matters, but you seem pretty determined to defend her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:34.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what exactly are we discussing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to fight Angel's clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make it disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:50.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she voluntarily created the clone, she should be able to erase it voluntarily too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just wait for Kanade to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:58.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if she could voluntarily erase it, would she be lying here like this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:01.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was most likely an unconscious command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she can't erase her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She had to do something, even if it meant getting stabbed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:13.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If she won't disappear, will this world be stuck with that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:17.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's ignoring us now, but she probably won't let us off the hook tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:22.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't act like the model students, it'll probably turn into another bloodbath like last night. {check}{血生臭い}{FOTC: Sounds fine to me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even through she isn't the student council president anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:30.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The directive to correct our actions has been embedded deep into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, she's aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we were to try taking her on, there wouldn't be enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we buy you time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:46.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to class and pretend you're paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen to anything the teacher says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take the lesson seriously, you'll disappear.{she doesn't say 'might' .. leave this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:55.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate on doing something else, just don't get caught by the clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray we can all meet up afterwards without losing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Girls Dormitories {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Angel Area}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know she splits in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need some way to get rid of the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Player?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a software manual...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a thick book, and all in English!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:18.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The number went up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:39.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, the clone was supposed to obey this order and vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you have to do to activate this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I just break the computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't make the clone vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:54.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just rewrite it into a program I do understand!{LOOOL}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Delay {\fnNyala}-{\fn} 10 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:01.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:10.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,10 seconds feels a long time when you're waiting.{ADD :D}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't I able to make it less than 10 seconds?{who knows.. you wrote it apparently...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, that should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:21.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:25.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Howling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:28.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the clone make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I delete it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've been careful so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should keep alterations to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Button Yuri clicks: Shut Down (lit: Shut down option {\fnNyala}-{\fn} which sounds wrong in Japanese as well as english :D)}{FOTC: I thought it's called "Standby Ready" or something these days. Vista does Hibernate.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:47.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Angel just needs to use Harmonics, and the Absorb skill will activate and re{\fnNyala}-{\fn}merge the clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We screwed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she just went out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:01.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade promised she'd stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She promised that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by this mess, we can only assume she was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You! What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:11.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just rewrote a program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If she uses her power again, the ability I added in will activate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the clone will re{\fnNyala}-{\fn}merge with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a quick patch though...{付け焼刃}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the enemy moved faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the clone hides her, there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:36.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,While avoiding Angel's brutal gaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:39.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It took all of our effort just to pretend to take lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'll come down to how long the diversion lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By diversion, you mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:46.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you join GirlDeMo in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I admire Iwasawa{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,GirlDeMo is supposed to be a diversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:53.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, I can't keep such a scary enemy distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your senior! I should be the one getting mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My senior? Well sorry then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might wet myself during the performance, but I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the determination, but I don't need you to yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do what we can for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:11.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battlefront{\fnNyala}-{\fn}wide order:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Collect witness reports of Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yo, check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moonwalk, it's a moonwalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Head spin!{*facepalm*}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Gym interior}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:25.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From the information we managed to gather, there's a good chance she's being held captive in Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's the case, it'll be in the deepest area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the area we detonated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:30.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The traps are still set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:36.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most dangerous, farthest location from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go down there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:42.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time we pretty much got wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first person who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep singing even if I pee myself, for everyone's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that monster strikes, the diversionary squad will be wiped out instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go without a diversion this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in openly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,While fighting Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:00.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:07.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is to descend into Guild and recapture the original Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Guild Accessway B4}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see the traps we fell for last time are still inactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:27.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:32.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... If we run into Angel here, I might wet myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:32.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Care, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:41.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Care, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:46.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, she's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have handguns!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:00.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her before she recovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we'll get this done faster than planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's also a clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there more than one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear the enemy is growing in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As a side note, that guy got done in first again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:27.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the one behind us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with the enemy in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're low on ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take up my rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:49.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:56.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who doesn't make it gets left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:01.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:02.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got two brutal Angels now.{FOTC: 残酷な天使のように　少年よ神話になれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:20.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is worse than the last Operation Descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:26.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The clones can use Hand Sonic and Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they can use Harmonics too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:32.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're all imbeciles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With the exception of Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you our current problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two problems:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First, how many clones are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If a clone can make a clone, there is no upper bound on the number. {FOTC: And we note monotonality, O(2^n).}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:53.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then besides those two, there might be another ten, twenty, or more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:58.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but Yuri changed the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The clones should go back, shouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just wait for them to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:04.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the second problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:11.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they cloned themselves before the program was changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignorant fools. You've finally realized?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're grand nobility, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:28.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if she knew we'd come after her and started making clones,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,then came down here to lure us in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:31.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, a trap.{FOTC: I like mine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are already two behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't win against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:43.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are probably countless below.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:46.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're sealed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't replenish our ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're just waiting to be taken out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she plan to do with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it, she wants us to obey the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's her mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She just wants us to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect plan to get rid of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:05.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Guild Accessway B10}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A third one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:28.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita 5th Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go while I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that line, acting like some cool guy on the brink of death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:46.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go while we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Matsushita 5th Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:52.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let Matsushita{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun's sacrifice go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Guild Accessway B11}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:05.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him, we know that that's the best way to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:09.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel is small, so that's the best way to stop her from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:14.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's stupidly strong, a Judo pin will hold her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we can finally use what he taught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:22.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, for each clone, one of us will be sacrificed and the rest will move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice one and move on?{Only a sacrifice!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:29.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we can save the original, we can save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Guild Accessway B12}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:34.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A fourth clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.{FOTC: NO TK DON'T!}{Norg: (￣ー￣)ﾆﾔﾘ }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:38.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get chance and luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:49.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this last{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chapter{\fnNyala}-{\fn}of{\fnNyala}-{\fn}a{\fnNyala}-{\fn}shonen{\fnNyala}-{\fn}manga scenario?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the time has come to show this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:01.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm gonna let myself get scared here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So shallow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So shallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you will realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:27.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, in that dark corner, a lonely girl is calling out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, that won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:32.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make you laugh—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oyama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He just misunderstood me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll go next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:50.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,<sign: Guild Accessway B15 >
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many is this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to survive to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's the feeling I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you need to carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to go, hurry up and go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow soon, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it, do you like him or hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< sign: Guild lowest point {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Ground Zero >
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Guild was before we blew it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to descend straight to the lowest level.{最下層}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun and Yui, you look for the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:40.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you find her, get her to activate Harmonics. {check}{Norg: lit is encourage her to activate Harmonics, but it sounds better as it is.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should fight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun already told you right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too weak to be of any use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only hope this is our last operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:00.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did Yui go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a scream for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel got her, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save her soon though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only two survivors again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, stop standing around and find the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, she's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Howling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{FUCK YEAH ASSASSIN'S CREED STYLE BABY}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't pass out...{気絶・・・しない}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you through my earplugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up. {check}{ほら　観念なさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My next knife here's going to take care of your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:57.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:07.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:13.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the Battlefront came here and gave their lives to find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:15.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:20.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade, I'm sorry to push you, but I need you to use one of your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can use Harmonics again, everyone will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:28.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will your body hold out if you use it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Harmonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you altered my program.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:46.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all of you are going to return to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:49.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That many of us ruthless clones are going to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as clones, we have our own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:56.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:57.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be incorporated into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:02.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits of all the clones you attacked will return to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:05.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When she takes in all those at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:12.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:31.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:37.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:40.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,<preview>
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:19.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:19.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time that's happened to Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:19.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no choice but to bear through it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:21.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to undress me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:21.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:22.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility is about 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:22.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.05,0:24:22.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone hit her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:23.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:22.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's coming to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.36,0:24:22.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:25.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side is God on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.68,0:24:25.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.83,0:24:27.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember everything.
